function Start(flGameTime)
	if boss_at_blocker == false then
		local tWolfBoss = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("CMP_Scos_MoordaineLodge_WolfBoss")
		if #tWolfBoss > 0 then
			idActor = tWolfBoss[1]
			Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(P_UNSTOPPABLE, "Unstoppable", idActor)
			Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(P_PASS, "MAIN", idActor)
			Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationConstantSpeed(idActor, WOLF_ESCAPE_POINT, Hydra.MOVE_RATE_SPRINT, true)
			Hydra.ActorMergeAIState(idActor, AI_BOSSRUN, idActor, 0)
			Hydra.ActorAddAITarget(idActor, ID_BOSS_RUNTO, true)
		end
	end
end

local function HunterAmbush(idGizmo)

	Hydra.ActorsEnableLinkedByActor(idGizmo)
	local tDestroy = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idGizmo, "Destroyable")
	for i, idActor in ipairs(tDestroy) do
		Hydra.Wait(0.1)
		Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idActor, false)
		Hydra.ActorKill(idActor)
	end

end
